                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2701Dawit">Psalter</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <note>Psalm 118 does not contain the spiritual meanings of the Hebrew letters, but it seems that space was left for them to be written and then they never were</note>
